{"tid":1050691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法院頒令學聯可收回八樓舊址 「自治八樓」成員稱真正公義在民間","createTime":"2019-03-07T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T03:18:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c76dc46d351f7ac638b9ff7f16123ad3c9b3696","tid":1050691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"法院頒令學聯可收回八樓舊址 「自治八樓」成員稱真正公義在民間<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190306/59336244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59336244&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=3d61cd4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59336244&h=e9228122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190306/59336244</a><br />\n<br />\n學聯於千禧年後內部現分歧，2006年其屬下社運資源中心宣佈「自治」，推動基進社會運動，因使用旺角金輪大廈8樓A室學聯舊址，故通稱「自治八樓」。至2017年7月學聯代表會決定收回8樓單位，其後更以業主身份向區域法院興訟收樓。案件今提訊，八樓成員未有派代表抗辯，司法常務官根據簡易程序，頒下學聯尋求的命令，下令單位佔用人離開。<br />\n<br />\n「自治八樓」雖未有抗辯，但有約30名成員及支持者到庭旁聽。成員在法院外稱，法庭頒令是意料之中，「自治八樓」未來會繼續參與和支持社會運動。他們認為學聯的學生官僚，有權在手，有錢打官司，一定會勝訴；惟真正的公義在民間，故將會舉辦一個「人民法庭」。<br />\n<br />\n有支援外勞和被逼遷基層租戶的人士到場聲援，質疑近年學生運動與社會運動分裂，而學聯現在更扮演逼遷的強權角色。<br />\n<br />\n學聯由「學聯及學生活動基金」代表興訟。學聯的代表律師表示，他們並不知道金輪8樓單位佔用人的具體身份。<br />\n<br />\n學聯現址位於旺角威特商業大廈9樓，因而有「九樓」之稱。「自治八樓」上月收到法庭傳票後發聲明，表示極之遺憾，揚言不打算出庭應訊，理由是不想「進入這套建制法律程序，及進入這個並非事實的業主及佔用人的關係」，並批評九樓以行政建制手段來處理團體內部矛盾，要求九樓取消訴訟，廣邀持份者民主協商。有關聲明亦有呈堂，司法常務官鑑於八樓成員不抗辯，最終不作訟費命令。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCMP394/19】"},{"pid":"66ebe582a1db6c536d7fc860db6fff980e24013e","tid":1050691,"uid":550,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"八樓班友已經係中二病末期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公義在民間咁佢地訓街都得啦"},{"pid":"c23eaed0a7a30e55a44673c6010cfc7939478395","tid":1050691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1875a715f2ddade00a3e1df8071db6168fea1215","tid":1050691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ed05ce99845e1878f67a87bebf573f2ddaa62e","tid":1050691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a79957c26ce836e981422c99641e513096ea9d7","tid":1050691,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報咁偏頗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d416651c104abfa702392ec88807705d3919f14","tid":1050691,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"想問自治八樓咁耐以黎做過啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n又想知點解學聯隔左11年先收翻？"},{"pid":"c37275abae143c841642320abf7f49221386b6a9","tid":1050691,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"收番左八樓係咪以周竪峰為首本土派終於開始搞革命？"},{"pid":"32cecb3691c9baa6e8dcd8e3bbd0a0c767064ba3","tid":1050691,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"以後都無私竇420<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d5ba4ec2719aef865fd4ea7c8e89460b65ef92","tid":1050691,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"何解班人可以一直霸住個單位<br />\n佢又唔係業主<br />\n自己換左把鎖所以話事?身體自主既私竇?"},{"pid":"07099e9aa2047733d31c1a3db93c7f5a84e50cc8","tid":1050691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}